{"tid":868304,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[大家研究下] 呢個年代生小朋友對你嚟講重唔重要?","createTime":"2018-10-19T10:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T10:18:56.000Z","uid":217326,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f56bd2b275d0a66709c9f8cd9b676d14c3e693","tid":868304,"uid":217326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:56:47.000Z","msg":"結婚生仔以傳統嚟講都係一代一代人會發生嘅事。但去到今日今日呢個年代，我見有D人結婚唔生小朋友，有D人就好渴求組織家庭，但樓價高收入有限亦成了一個問題。對於有冇後代其實大家點睇? 有冇人可以分享下? 會唔會因為傳統或父母關係，屋企人就會希望你未來生番一件或兩件?<br />\n<br />\n最近聽好多身邊朋友講到，結咗婚都要分開住，莫講話有冇得生，連基本生活同人工問題處處。有冇巴絲打可以分享下? 有冇後代其實對你嚟講重唔重要呢? 如果無，你又會用咩心態去看? 如果有，你自己本身又會點諗?"},{"pid":"3ec58239ff187438846b106f803367ff42812d7d","tid":868304,"uid":41355,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"生佢出黎受苦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f3be29117bc60739a20004804e7771bab28114","tid":868304,"uid":74262,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e2464dc409c1a2d33c2fd6bd5010230cf2e45fa","tid":868304,"uid":54387,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"好重要!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定唔生, 呢點好重要"},{"pid":"d9546af103d23a0a8ae8ed8cef60f875931ea5e0","tid":868304,"uid":50801,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:03:28.000Z","msg":"地球好多人，資源唔夠分，生佢出黎等佢爭餐飽？<br />\n仲有識生唔識教搞左好多問題出黎<br />\n我真心覺得生細路要攞牌，同埋仔女對父母做任何事都係免刑責，個細路係父母教出黎，有咩後果自己受返好應該"},{"pid":"f0015ea66a67c4a1c8be5e0e00b23cd9974b7566","tid":868304,"uid":217326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53f3be29117bc60739a20004804e7771bab28114","tid":868304,"uid":74262,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"咁強調呢樣嘢，似乎有故事先有商量喎"},{"pid":"21342758af55badfe2e45e1035c9e9caa5df4c59","tid":868304,"uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:03:36.000Z","msg":"生你老母，個人資產淨值冇一個 Billion 都唔好生，唔想睇住下一個絕望、冇夢想嘅生命誕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07abb4e31733e8ff18e1a2c69efa678b8e4a767","tid":868304,"uid":24752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:03:40.000Z","msg":"唔生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2d8556e58ca046035976f2a9a67079d3b27dea","tid":868304,"uid":114275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:03:47.000Z","msg":"你可以先撫心自問 你生活得開唔開心？<br />\n<br />\n如果唔開心 咁你點有信心生個仔日後會開心？"},{"pid":"e7b7087e0c9a74ea381594e61614be67bafa51a1","tid":868304,"uid":217326,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9e2464dc409c1a2d33c2fd6bd5010230cf2e45fa","tid":868304,"uid":54387,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"好重要!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定唔生, 呢點好重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:04:57.000Z","msg":"咁你係心理上覺得生係好重要，然後一定唔生係行動嘅思想證明?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a97f9bb888e028456f8d468f8cd0ca7d1aea73e","tid":868304,"uid":213227,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"我自己生咗個女之後我就唔希望我個女第時生小朋友<br />\n不過生唔生佢自己選擇"},{"pid":"be71c010563bd81cb06958a3c564862086124d95","tid":868304,"uid":8773,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:05:18.000Z","msg":"冇父幹既我，唔想比佢話冇父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7487c29e782ecf071a1a21b8b43cc6742e9d1cfe","tid":868304,"uid":169220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:06:21.000Z","msg":"緊係唔生啦 窮人生咩仔"},{"pid":"b4805416db0a2aaa56bd31d544a6562f06ad79a0","tid":868304,"uid":217326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a97f9bb888e028456f8d468f8cd0ca7d1aea73e","tid":868304,"uid":213227,"li